replies.body:
I have tried to play league throughout the past 2 years but I have had this issue. I still cannot find a post anywhere with a solution. I'd love to have riot fix this issue soon so I could play with the new content. Or give me the old client back because I didn't lag at all with that one. (I don't have a toaster for a computer either, the lag is entirely because of their client). 

I sit at 60-70 ms the entire game with around 150 fps, yet all my abilities are slightly delayed and I lag as if i have 500 ms or 30 fps. It's in weird small bursts. By late game it's less severe ( if I can sit through a game to late game ).
pls help, riot. {{summoner:7}}
